# order-service

## Project Overview

Order management microservice built with Node.js and TypeScript.

## Tech Stack

- Node.js 20
- TypeScript 5.5
- Fastify 4
- Prisma (ORM)
- Zod (validation)
- Vitest (testing)

## Project Structure

```
src/
├── routes/        # HTTP route handlers
├── services/      # Business logic
└── repos/         # Data access layer
tests/             # Test files
```

## Commands

- `pnpm dev` — Start development server
- `pnpm build` — Compile TypeScript
- `pnpm test` — Run tests
- `pnpm lint` — Run linter
- `pnpm db:migrate` — Run database migrations
- `pnpm db:generate` — Generate Prisma client
